# RPG 配置 DSL 参考

## 条件 Condition

```text
level>=5
quest:quest_ch01_intro=completed
flag:story_ch01_met_master=true
item:item_wolf_fang>=3
faction:fac_qingyun_rep>=100
```

组合：

```text
level>=5 && flag:map_blackwood_unlocked=true
quest:quest_a=completed || quest:quest_b=completed
```

## 奖励 Reward_List

```text
xp:100|silver:50|item:item_heal_pill:2|equipment:equip_iron_sword:1|reputation:fac_qingyun:20
```

## 效果 Effect_List

```text
damage:physical:1.2|status:status_bleed:3:60|heal:hp:0.3
```

## 属性修正 Stat_Modifier_List

```text
ATK:+10|DEF:-5|SPD:*1.1|CRIT_RATE:+5
```

## 掉落 Drop 简写

```text
silver:10:80|item:iron_sword:1:10|equipment:equip_bronze_blade:1:5
```

推荐长期拆成 `Loot_Tables` + `Loot_Entries`，简写只适合原型阶段。
